NAME
----
xe-host-shutdown-agent - Stop the xapi service on host

SYNOPSIS
--------
*xe host-shutdown-agent*

DESCRIPTION
-----------
*xe host-shutdown-agent* attempts to stop the xapi service on host. To restart the xapi service, use *xe-toolstart-restart* or */etc/init.d/xapi start*.

EXAMPLES
--------
To stop the xapi service on host:
	*xe host-shutdown-agent*

SEE ALSO
--------
*xe help host-shutdown-agent*, *xe host-list*(1), *xe-toolstack-restart*
